    songs: ["Some Enchanted Evening","m Gonna Wash That Man Right Outa My Hair\", \"Bali Ha","A Cockeyed Optimist","Bloody Mary","There Is Nothin’ Like a Dame","Bali Ha’i","I’m Gonna Wash That Man Right Outa My Hair","A Wonderful Guy","Younger Than Springtime","Happy Talk","Honey Bun","You’ve Got to Be Carefully Taught","This Nearly Was Mine","Dites-moi (pourquoi)","Twin Soliloquies","Bloody Mary (Is the Girl I Love)","(I’m in Love with) A Wonderful Guy","Soft Shoe Dance"],
    tonyWins: 10,
