    producer: "Richard Rodgers and Oscar Hammerstein II",
    songs: ["All Kinds of People","The Tide Pool","Everybody’s Got a Home but Me","A Lopsided Bus","Bums’ Opera","Fauna’s Song","Babaloo","The Man I Used to Be","Sweet Thursday","Suzy Is a Good Thing","All at Once You Love Her","The Happiest House on the Block","The Party That We’re Gonna Have Tomorrow Night","The Masquerade Ball at the Flophouse","The Party Gets Going","We Are a Gang of Witches","Will You Marry Me?","Thinkin’","How Long?","The Next Time It Happens","girls"],
