    songs: ["Seventy-Six Trombones","Till There Was You","Ya Got Trouble","Gary, Indiana","Rock Island","Trouble","Goodnight My Someone","Sincere","The Sadder-but-Wiser Girl","Marian the Librarian","My White Knight","Wells Fargo Wagon","Shipoopi","Lida Rose"],
    tonyWins: 5,
