    songs: ["s Coming Up Roses\", ",", \"Rose","Some People","Let Me Entertain You","Small World","Little Lamb","You’ll Never Get Away from Me","If Momma Was Married","All I Need Is the Girl","Everything’s Coming Up Roses","Together","You Gotta Have a Gimmick","Rose’s Turn","May We Entertain You","Traveling","Baby June and Her Newsboys","Mr. Goldstone, I Love You","Dainty June and Her Farmboys","Madame Rose’s Toreadorables","Together, Wherever We Go","You Gotta Get a Gimmick"],
