    theatre: "Mark Hellinger Theatre",
    composer: "Jimmy McHugh, etc.",
    lyricist: "Dorothy Fields, etc.  Conception: Ralph G. Allen & Harry Rigby Sketches: Ralph G. Allen Producers: Terry Allen Kramer & Harry Rigby Directors: Ernest Flatt, Rudy Tronto",
    director: "Ernest Flatt, Rudy Tronto",
