    description: "The untold story of the witches of Oz: Elphaba, the misunderstood green girl, and Glinda, the popular blonde. A generation-defining exploration of friendship, power, and the nature of good and evil.",
    funFact: "Wicked lost the Best Musical Tony to Avenue Q, one of the biggest upsets in Tony history. It didn\\'t matter: the show has grossed over $1.5 billion on Broadway.",
    synopsis: "Wicked is loosely based on novelist Gregory MaGuire’s inventive exploration of The Wizard of Oz, which is told from the perspective of the witches. Stephen Schwartz was so enthusiastic after reading it he sought and obtained the theatrical rights and adapted it in collaboration with book writer Winnie Holtzman.\n\nThe Shiz University, presided over by headmistress Madame Morrible, is where student witches the noble green Elphaba (Idina Menzel), “The Wicked Witch of the East,” and the ambitious Glinda (Kristin Chenoweth), “The Good Witch of the North,” meet and eventually clash. The origins of Toto, the munchkins, the Tin Man, the Cowardly Lion, the Scarecrow, the Yellow Brick Road, and the Wizard are all explained.",
